Activity
Purpose: Base class for all mindfulness activities.
Responsibilities:

Store the name, description, and duration of an activity
Display start and end messages
Provide a countdown spinner during activities
Define the structure for running any activity


--------------------------------------------
|              Activity                    |
--------------------------------------------
| - _name_RP : string                     |
| - _description_RP : string              |
| - _duration_RP : int                    |
--------------------------------------------
| + Activity(name, description)           |
| + SetDuration_RP(duration)              |
| + GetDuration_RP() : int               |
| + DisplayStartMessage_RP()             |
| + DisplayEndMessage_RP()               |
| - Spinner_RP(seconds)                  |
| + RunActivity_RP() [abstract]          |
--------------------------------------------



BreathingActivity
